Role	Suggested GPIOs
MOSI	GPIO 11, 13, 15
MISO	GPIO 12, 14
SCLK	GPIO 9, 10
CS	Any free pin (e.g. GPIO 5, 7, etc.)
DC / RST	Any free pin (e.g. GPIO 6, 16, 17)
You cannot use GPIO 19 or 20 unless USB is fully disabled in the build settings.


